  <h4 class="font-semibold">TL;DR</h4>
  <p>
    This EIP significantly reduces the gas costs for the <code>alt_bn128</code> curve operations (<code
      >ECADD</code
    >, <code>ECMUL</code>, and pairing checks) to reflect performance improvements in Ethereum
    clients like Geth and Parity.
  </p>

